snippet.title: JermaSlots: The Trailer
snippet.description:
Months in the making and it is nearly ready to go - here's the very COMPACT trailer for a COMPACT game about a slot machine themed after everyone's favorite ass eater, Jerma985.

Find the game here when it comes out soon (completely free):
